Bullring
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:Rugby Park, New Plymouth - a happy  coincidence of allusions - to the Taranaki Mascot, Ferdinand the Bull, and to Taranaki's most popular player and captain, Mark "Bull" Allen
